I dont even know what to say, the only reason I gave it one star was because you cant rate lower! 

the service was horrible! the food was low quality, the atmosphere horrible. Im sure this place may have been nice MAYBE in the 80's buut... that was a long time ago. 

if you want to pay 100 bucks for a meal your better off getting at applebees be my guest. (or should I say THEIR guest)
